@startuml scoreboard WSS
title WebSocket Live Updates & Heartbeat (Multi-Client Broadcast)
autonumber

actor "Client A" as CA
actor "Client B" as CB
actor "Client C" as CC
participant "WebSocket Server" as WSS
collections "Redis Pub/Sub" as REDIS
participant "Score Service" as SCORE

== Connection Phase ==
CA -> WSS: Connect WS /api/v1/scoreboard/live?token=JWT
WSS -> WSS: (Optional) Validate JWT
WSS --> CA: Connection established (101 Switching Protocols)
WSS -> CA: Initial leaderboard snapshot (Top 10)

CB -> WSS: Connect WS /api/v1/scoreboard/live?token=JWT
WSS --> CB: Connection established (101)
WSS -> CB: Initial leaderboard snapshot

CC -> WSS: Connect WS /api/v1/scoreboard/live?token=JWT
WSS --> CC: Connection established (101)
WSS -> CC: Initial leaderboard snapshot

note over WSS
WebSocket Server maintains
a pool of active connections
end note

== Live Update Broadcasting ==
loop Continuous updates
    SCORE -> REDIS: PUBLISH leaderboard:update\n{ userId, newScore, changedRanks }
    REDIS -> WSS: Event received
    WSS -> WSS: Debounce (<=500ms) &\nprocess differential update
    
    par Broadcast to all connected clients
        WSS -> CA: leaderboard:update { diff }
        WSS -> CB: leaderboard:update { diff }
        WSS -> CC: leaderboard:update { diff }
    end
    
    note right of WSS
    Only send differential updates
    (changed ranks) not full leaderboard
    end note
end

== Heartbeat Mechanism ==
loop Every 30 seconds
    par Ping all clients
        WSS -> CA: PING
        WSS -> CB: PING
        WSS -> CC: PING
    end
    
    alt Client A responds
        CA -> WSS: PONG
    else Timeout (10s)
        WSS -> WSS: Close connection for Client A
        note right: Remove from active pool
    end
    
    alt Client B responds
        CB -> WSS: PONG
    else Timeout (10s)
        WSS -> WSS: Close connection for Client B
    end
    
    alt Client C responds
        CC -> WSS: PONG
    else Timeout (10s)
        WSS -> WSS: Close connection for Client C
    end
end

== Client Disconnection ==
CA -> WSS: Close connection
WSS -> WSS: Remove Client A from pool
WSS --> CA: Connection closed (1000)

note over CA,CC
Clients can reconnect anytime
and receive current leaderboard state
end note

@enduml
